t: "They ask you ňĻO Prophetňļ regarding the Hour, ‚ÄúWhen will it be?‚ÄĚ Say, ‚ÄúThat knowledge is only with my Lord. He alone will reveal it when the time comes. It is too tremendous for the heavens and the earth and will only take you by surprise.‚ÄĚ They ask you as if you had full knowledge of it. Say, ‚ÄúThat knowledge is only with God, but most people do not know.‚ÄĚ"